      "options": [
        "Lactic acid",
        "Ethanol and CO2",
        "Only water",
        "Only CO2"
      ],
      "explanation": "Yeast performs anaerobic respiration (fermentation): C6H12O6 -> 2C2H5OH + 2CO2 + Energy. This is used in baking and brewing industries."
    },
